Accessory : Hunting Dog

A hunting dog to sniff out and track down nearby
dinosaurs, or just to provide some companionship.
Your dog will howl when it can sense nearby prey,
and will attemp to lead you toward it. Please
note, the dog can inadvertently frighten
dinosaurs, so use the come and stay commands
wisely. Causing grevious bodily harm to DHC
hunting dogs will incur hefty fines.

